Q2) Sum of N whole numbers?
whole numbers starts from 0 so N whole numbers are

0, 1, 2, 3, .... N-1
n-1(n-1+1)/2 = (n-1)*(n)/2 = n(n-1)/2
Ans - n*(n-1)/2

